snippet.textDisplay:
What I gathered from this trailer:

The NPCs are all self aware and sentient, but Guy may be the first to display agency. Since he's also marked as essential, like all NPCs in this PVP world, he is unable to be killed.

It looks like a group of players have discovered this and are exploiting it to their advantage.


I suspect the developers will be after him, since Guy has the potential to inspire a world of unkillable non-paying players messing with their in-world economy and events.
